<segment id="91" parent="1093" relname="span">and White mates in three</segment>
<segment id="92" parent="91" relname="elaboration">( 19 . Nh6+ double check Kh8 20 . Qg8+ Rxg8 21 . Nf7 # ) .</segment>
<segment id="93" parent="1093" relname="evidence">[ 3 ]</segment>
<segment id="94" parent="1092" relname="evidence">[ 4 ]</segment>
<segment id="95" parent="1096" relname="span">Moheshchunder had a flair for dramatic play</segment>
<segment id="96" parent="95" relname="elaboration">evidenced by his sacrifices in this King 's Indian Defence game</segment>
<segment id="97" parent="1097" relname="span">( a variation</segment>
<segment id="98" parent="97" relname="elaboration">known today as the Four Pawns Attack ) :</segment>
